{"tid":1948341,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"缺少咗連儂牆，無論條街多人少人，我地都會失去同部分手足嘅連繫","createTime":"2020-03-29T03:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T13:39:04.000Z","uid":211994,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f19fe48c8cc37c0671c0083979c40cdf5daeee","tid":1948341,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:01:39.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇見過以下嘅情景<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Of8r4XS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOf8r4XS.jpg&h=2bd56c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場運動唔止年青人，中年同老年嘅手足都有參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地平時接收資訊嘅渠道就係屋企樓下嘅連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得有次銀髮手足搞大遊行，聽講就係靠連儂牆互相通報消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地如果只集中喺連登同tg傾我地嘅計劃同行動嘅話，呢一班手足就可以接收唔切，甚至係根本唔知我地將要做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解決方法有三：<br />\n<br />\n1.落街貼文宣，如果要痴就要痴大張啲清晰啲，最好就係A4 size，資訊型文宣會比口號式文宣好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.多啲同你身邊嘅叔叔姨姨公公婆婆分享下最近有咩活動，有咩資訊要知，當然幫佢地開個tg ac就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.唔好只係喺連登tg發播消息，多啲喺fb上分享文宣<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有咩睇法同建議呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊嚟傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咩話！？</span>你話唔知邊度有文宣攞嚟share？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣喇mention la app：<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/mention-la-%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3%E5%96%87/id1488286618?l=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fmention-la-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%2596%2587%2Fid1488286618%3Fl%3Den&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=911d1b14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/mention-la-%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3%E5%96%87/id1488286618?l=en</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣tg channel，咁多個月一直都有更新㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HK_Schedule\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHK_Schedule&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=d79014c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HK_Schedule</a>"},{"pid":"55ce3126f8cc7f66217304ead2a922e19f3ec9f7","tid":1948341,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:01:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e201bdcab6eb8103488aceb25b7e8e91d5b53b3","tid":1948341,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:02:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8347a0820cb8eed2a6a266b02590105341be1615","tid":1948341,"uid":211994,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"連儂牆要進化喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r7ebwJ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr7ebwJ1.jpg&h=8ab2583d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"406d96e3ce2dd6df3dd7f3d750fd0b3810beab90","tid":1948341,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:03:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d71757449553853d2c5986088fa56c8a13d64b0","tid":1948341,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:04:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"283448c74ad96830a94c9bbc95515c879d1d8cc0","tid":1948341,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:04:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30826842280cab7fed1b83f340810efaa0e78012","tid":1948341,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:06:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f14bf1cf2b97ad7d0edc23cccbbd3f9bfad92544","tid":